These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, zombie, action
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, hamster, horse
1. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the owner of the hamster##7
2. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
3. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Movie-Genre   | action | zombie | time-travel |
| Pet           | hamster  | horse     | hedgehog  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, techno, punk
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, ship, skateboard
1. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere between the fan of punk and the person driving the ship##7
3. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | techno | hip-hop | punk |
| Transport     | ship       | skateboard     | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk, milk
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, boat, scooter
1. the person driving the boat is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person driving the tram##7
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage    | tea | soy-milk | milk  |
| Transport   | scooter  | boat  | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, librarian, designer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, adventure, horror
1. the analyst is somewhere between the person watching horror movies and the librarian##7
2. the person watching adventure movies is not the analyst##6
3. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching adventure movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Job           | librarian | analyst | designer     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure    | musical          | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, house, blues
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, jet-ski, trike
1. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere between the person driving the trike and the fan of house##7
2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | trance      | blues     | house   |
| Transport     | trike | jet-ski | roller |

