.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, ambient, metal
There are 3 different nationalities: american, polish, brazilian
1. the american is on the left or right of the polish##3
2. the polish is somewhere to the left of the american##5
3. the fan of ambient is on the right of the brazilian##1
4. the fan of ambient is somewhere between the brazilian and the fan of funk##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | ambient     | funk     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | polish | american |

