.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, rabbit, bird
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, swimming, cycling
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the person who's sport is climbing##7
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Pet     | bird       | rabbit      | snake       |
| Sport   | climbing | cycling | swimming |

