2. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the person watching adventure movies and the pilot##7
3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Job           | fisherman | photographer  | pilot |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | satire | family      |

