.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, gardening, hiking
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, writer, mechanic
1. the mechanic is not the person who's hobby is hiking##6
2. the writer is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the designer is somewhere between the writer and the person who's hobby is gardening##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | gardening | hiking | singing   |
| Job     | mechanic    | designer  | writer |

