.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, lemonade
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, water-polo, rugby
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's sport is water-polo##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | lemonade    | water |
| Sport      | rugby | lacrosse | water-polo |

