.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
There 3 different types of food: banana, lettuce, nectarine
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, spy, horror
1. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the person eating banana##7
3. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food          | banana  | nectarine       | lettuce     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | documentary | spy |

