2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the fan of gospel is somewhere between the fan of hip-hop and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |  3   |
