.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-14::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, cauliflower, pineapple
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, skateboard, van
1. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person eating cauliflower##5
2. the person driving the van is the person eating cauliflower##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the person driving the van and the person eating pear##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food        | cauliflower | pineapple | pear |
| Transport   | van  | skateboard       | trike      |

