.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, soy-milk
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, dancer, writer
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the scientist##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the dancer##7
3. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage   | juice      | soy-milk     | iced-tea |
| Job        | writer | scientist | dancer    |

 